---
title: Scandi-Style Tilapia with Apple and Pickled Onion Salad
description: Summer flavours, made cozy! Dilly buttered potatoes are paired with honey and mustard-glazed salmon. Pickled red onions are the perfect salad topper for a tangy, puckery pop!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220614_R1011_W31_CA_RF154356-3_KB_Main_low_edit_salat-406c8823.jpg
